author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
Black Panther and Cosmic Ghost Rider join the fight against the immortal Super Villain Annihilus!

Play MARVEL Cosmic Invasion later this year on PC and Consoles:
https://www.dotemu.com/games/marvel-cosmic-invasion/

After Annihilus has launched an unprecedented attack across the galaxy, Cosmic Ghost Rider can’t let that go unpunished!

Atop his Hell cycle, this wild incarnation of the Rider roars across the spaceways!

Evildoers beware: this Spirit of Stellar Vengeance punishes the guilty by wielding both hellfire and the Power Cosmic!

By his side, Black Panther, the stalwart leader of Wakanda, dashes into battle wearing King T’Challa’s vibranium-enhanced suit and sonic daggers. With peerless martial arts skills and strength, he’ll pounce on any threat or foe foolish enough to challenge him!

Black Panther and Cosmic Ghost Rider join Captain America, Wolverine, Spider-Man, Storm, Phyla-Vell, Venom, Nova, She-Hulk, Rocket Raccoon, Silver Surfer and Beta Ray Bill in a star-spanning ad
title: MARVEL Cosmic Invasion – Black Panther and Cosmic Ghost Rider Character Reveal

description:
